TASK:
- building a python module for talking with UMTS sticks
- building a PyGTK GUI for using the sticks

REQUIRED:
- python module serial
	- debian package python-serial
	- http://pyserial.sourceforge.net/

TESTED WITH:
- "o2 prepaid surfstick" == Huawei 1550 UMTS

DONE:
- sending raw commands
- PIN authentication

